snippet.title: Freelancer Amber
snippet.description: What is up people of the internet?! Freelancer Amber here!! I react to mostly Rooster Teeth content such as RWBY and Red vs Blue, I also react to other content. Hopefully in the future, I can stream games. If you like to see me react to the funniest, most badass, weirdest, saddest or terrifying videos feel free to check out my channel and also feel free to subscribe. Don't make me have my dogs give you the puppy-dog eyes.
